From: Neil Armstrong <neil.armstrong@linaro.org>
Date: Wed, 16 Aug 2023 10:06:47 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Bluetooth: qca: use switch case for soc type behavior
Git-commit: 691d54d0f7cb14baac1ff4af210d13c0e4897e27
Patch-mainline: v6.6-rc1
